### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/healthz

### List images
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/images

### Pull image
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/images/pull
content-type: application/json

{
  "image": "nginx:latest"
}

### Run container (auto-assign host port)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers/run
content-type: application/json

{
  "image": "nginx:latest",
  "container_port": 80,
  "host_port": 0,
  "name": "nginx-demo",
  "wait_ready": true,
  "health_path": "/"
}

### List containers
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers

### Inspect container
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers/{{containerId}}

### Logs (last 100)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers/{{containerId}}/logs?tail=100

### Logs (follow)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers/{{containerId}}/logs?follow=true&tail=100

### Exec inside container
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers/{{containerId}}/exec
content-type: application/json

{
  "command": ["ls", "-la", "/"],
  "workdir": "/",
  "tty": false
}

### Proxy GET with query
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/proxy/{{containerId}}/api/items?page=1&limit=10

### Proxy POST JSON
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/proxy/{{containerId}}/api/items
content-type: application/json

{
  "name": "example"
}

### Stop container
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers/{{containerId}}/stop

### Start container
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers/{{containerId}}/start

### Remove container
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/containers/{{containerId}}
